| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4196 — Recovery Inhibition (bianlian)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: a8de0bb0-676e-5c50-9a6d-878fd5c2c414"
